nl_querry: Write the full name of the member who spent money for water, veggie tray and supplies and include the cost of it. full name refers to first_name, last name; spent money for refers expense description; expense_description = 'Water, Veggie tray, supplies'
llm_querry: SELECT `T1`.`first_name`, `T1`.`last_name`, `T2`.`expense_description`, `T2`.`cost` FROM `member` AS `T1` JOIN `expense` AS `T2` ON `T1`.`member_id` = `T2`.`link_to_member` WHERE `T2`.`expense_description` = 'Water, Veggie tray, supplies'
gold_querry: SELECT T2.first_name, T2.last_name, T1.cost FROM expense AS T1 INNER JOIN member AS T2 ON T1.link_to_member = T2.member_id WHERE T1.expense_description = 'Water, Veggie tray, supplies'
